{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|𢇍|斤|t1=to cut|t2=axe|ls=ic}}.

Before the Qin dynasty, this character was written as {{zh-l|𠸿}} or {{zh-l|𠜷}}.

{{zh-hanzi}}

# to [[break]]; to [[snap]]
#* {{zh-x|他 說 他 的 手臂 斷 了。|He said that he'd broken his arm.}}
#* {{zh-x|枝 樹枝 斷{tyun5} 咗。|A tree branch '''broke'''.|C}}
# to [[cut off]]; to [[sever]]; to [[interrupt]]
#* {{zh-x|通話 斷 了。|The line has gone dead.}}
# to [[give up]]; to [[abstain]] from; to [[quit]]
#* {{zh-x|斷 煙|to quit smoking}}
#* {{zh-x|在 孩子 三 個 月 大 時，她 給 孩子 斷 了 奶，並 開始 喂 奶粉。|She [[wean]]ed her baby when he was 3 months old and started him on powdered milk.}}

{{zh-hanzi}}

# to [[judge]]; to [[decide]]; to [[determine]]; to [[settle]]
#* {{zh-x|判斷|to decide, to determine}}
#* {{zh-x|這 個 案子 很 難 斷。|It is hard to '''judge''' this case.}}
# {{lb|zh|used in the negative}} [[absolutely]]; [[definitely]]; [[decidedly]]
# 29th [[tetragram]] of the [[Taixuanjing]]; "[[decisiveness]]" ([[𝌢]])
